02:03.100 --> 02:06.634
 <i>And now</i>
Married With Children
 <i>continues...</i>

02:06.634 --> 02:08.701
All right, ladies,
let's hear it!

02:08.701 --> 02:10.434
That was Zorro!

02:10.434 --> 02:13.601
He's got my ring.
What are going to do?

02:13.601 --> 02:15.400
Uh... treasure hunt!

02:18.601 --> 02:20.400
Hold it right there, ladies.

02:20.400 --> 02:22.367
Listen, we've got
to get backstage.

02:22.367 --> 02:26.901
We've got to get something
out of Zorro's pants.

02:26.901 --> 02:29.167
That old story again,
Mrs. Bundy.

02:29.167 --> 02:30.601
But this is
an emergency.

02:30.601 --> 02:31.801
Yeah, right.

02:31.801 --> 02:33.801
Look, lady,
we used to let women backstage

02:33.801 --> 02:35.133
until the big riot.

02:35.133 --> 02:37.133
Now nobody's
allowed back there.

02:37.133 --> 02:41.534
We call it
"The Bundy rule."

02:41.534 --> 02:43.033
It's my wedding ring.

02:43.033 --> 02:45.267
I want it back,
or I'll see you in court.

02:45.267 --> 02:46.767
I don't think so.

02:46.767 --> 02:48.567
You see,
"Troy's is not responsible

02:48.567 --> 02:52.067
for valuables lost
in any part of a dancer."

02:52.067 --> 02:55.334
Once again,
"The Bundy rule."

02:55.334 --> 02:58.067
What are we
going to do?

02:58.067 --> 03:01.167
I know! I'll write
Zorro a note.

03:01.167 --> 03:03.167
That's it!
He'll read it,

03:03.167 --> 03:06.200
He'll find my ring,
bring it over tomorrow,

03:06.200 --> 03:09.300
Steve will answer
the door, kill me...

03:09.300 --> 03:10.801
No, that won't work.

03:10.801 --> 03:12.801
I'll write a note,
but I'll give him

03:12.801 --> 03:15.801
your phone number
and address--

03:15.801 --> 03:17.601
that is,
if you don't mind.

03:17.601 --> 03:18.601
Sure, I don't mind,

03:18.601 --> 03:20.100
as long as he comes over

03:20.100 --> 03:23.567
before what's-his-name
gets home from work.

03:23.567 --> 03:30.334
Ooh!

03:30.334 --> 03:31.534
Oh, thanks, Peggy.

03:31.534 --> 03:35.367
You really are
the very best friend I've got.

