05:59.367 --> 06:00.868
Oh, and kids, remember!

06:00.868 --> 06:02.367
When you say hello,

06:02.367 --> 06:04.834
Grandpa is the one
with the hair.

06:06.968 --> 06:08.467
Any sign of Zorro?

06:08.467 --> 06:14.834
No, but I think I slept with
Speedy Gonzalez last night.

06:14.834 --> 06:16.734
Steve is going to go crazy.

06:16.734 --> 06:18.701
My wedding ring's
gone forever.

06:18.701 --> 06:20.200
Oh, Marcie, calm down.

06:20.200 --> 06:22.968
Men don't notice
things like that.

06:22.968 --> 06:24.501
Not Steven.

06:24.501 --> 06:26.000
He notices everything.

06:26.000 --> 06:29.200
Do you know what we do
in bed sometimes?

06:29.200 --> 06:31.267
Yeah, Bud tells us.

06:35.000 --> 06:36.033
Oh.

06:36.033 --> 06:37.534
Well, anyway,

06:37.534 --> 06:39.934
Steve and I lie in bed,

06:39.934 --> 06:42.934
put our ring fingers
together.

06:42.934 --> 06:45.434
We stare at
our wedding bands,

06:45.434 --> 06:47.934
then kiss.

06:47.934 --> 06:49.934
So Bud made that up

06:49.934 --> 06:51.200
about Little Bo Peep
and the cop?

06:56.133 --> 06:59.467
Yes, he did.

06:59.467 --> 07:00.968
Oh, what's the difference?

07:00.968 --> 07:05.868
Steve will never
pull me over again!

07:05.868 --> 07:09.901
How can I tell him
I lost my wedding ring?

07:09.901 --> 07:11.868
It's an irreplaceable symbol
of our love everlasting.

07:11.868 --> 07:13.901
Buy a cheap copy.

07:13.901 --> 07:16.601
Yeah!

